<para> To resolve this problem, insure that you do not pass <computeroutput>&lt;hostname&gt;::&lt;vnodename&gt;</computeroutput> in your connect parameters.
 Simply pass the vnode.
 Use of hostname should be reserved for instances in which the Ingres database resides on a remote machine.</para><para>If the problem persists with Multi-Tier drivers:</para><para>1.
 Install any Multi-Tier server components under the ingres uid.
